---
// HOME 클라이언트 로고월 — 카테고리당 8개 cap, 정적 데이터 (lib/client-logos.ts) 사용.
import { CLIENT_LOGO_GROUPS, getLogoPath } from "@/lib/client-logos";

const PER_SECTION = 8;

const grouped = CLIENT_LOGO_GROUPS.map((g) => ({
  ...g,
  items: g.items.slice(0, PER_SECTION),
})).filter((g) => g.items.length > 0);
---

<section class="bg-background">
  <div class="mx-[var(--divider-inset)] border-t border-foreground"></div>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[var(--container-max)] px-[var(--container-padding)] py-14 md:py-24">

    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted">
        Trusted by
      </p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 font-serif text-[clamp(28px,3.5vw,42px)] leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-foreground">
        함께해 온 기업들
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 space-y-14">
      {grouped.map((group) => (
        <div>
          <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted">
            {group.label}
          </p>
          <div class="mt-5 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4">
            {group.items.map((item) => (
              <div class="flex aspect-[16/7] items-center justify-center border border-line bg-white px-4 py-3 transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-foreground">
                <img
                  src={getLogoPath(group, item)}
                  alt={item.name}
                  class="max-h-full max-w-full object-contain"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 text-center">
      <p class="font-serif italic text-base text-muted break-keep">
        — 그 외 100여 클라이언트와 함께해 왔습니다.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/about/clients"
        class="mt-7 inline-block border-b border-foreground pb-1 text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-foreground transition-colors duration-200 ease-[var(--ease-out-soft)] hover:border-accent hover:text-accent"
      >
        View All Clients →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
